TITLE: Declaring a Message Command Interface for Middleware Filtering in Wolverine (C#)
DESCRIPTION: Defines the IAccountCommand interface with an AccountId property, used as a marker for applying middleware selectively in Wolverine. Facilitates type-based middleware registration, ensuring that specific middleware is only invoked for relevant message types. Requires implementations to expose a Guid property.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jasperfx/wolverine/blob/main/docs/guide/handlers/middleware.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
public interface IAccountCommand
{
    Guid AccountId { get; }
}
```

