TITLE: Configuring Marten and Wolverine with RabbitMQ for Durable Messaging in C#
DESCRIPTION: This snippet sets up a .NET WebApplication integrating Marten for persistence and Wolverine for messaging. It configures a PostgreSQL connection for Marten, enables Wolverine integration, defines retry policies, uses Marten for message storage, configures RabbitMQ for transport with durable inbox/outbox enabled globally, and auto-applies transactions. Requires Marten, Wolverine, Wolverine.Marten, Wolverine.RabbitMQ, and Oakton NuGet packages.
