TITLE: Registering Middleware by Message Type Using Configuration API in Wolverine (C#)
DESCRIPTION: Depicts how to register middleware globally for message types implementing a specific interface via the UseWolverine options configuration. The sample also demonstrates additional policies like FluentValidation registration and local publish route setup. Requires a configured builder.Host and presumes prior setup of corresponding middleware classes/types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jasperfx/wolverine/blob/main/docs/guide/handlers/middleware.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: csharp
