TITLE: Defining Request ID Middleware in C#
DESCRIPTION: Defines a static class `RequestIdMiddleware` with an `Apply` method. This middleware extracts a correlation ID from the `X-Correlation-ID` request header and applies it to the Wolverine `IMessageContext` if present. It depends on `HttpContext` and `IMessageContext` and is intended to propagate tracing information across requests and subsequent messages.
