DESCRIPTION: Implements a reusable continuation by subclassing UserDefinedContinuation, enabling custom error handling logic to run when processing fails. On execution, the policy examines if the failed envelope's message is a ShipOrder and sends a ShippingFailed message in response. Intended for registration as a secondary action in error policies, this approach encapsulates error response logic for reuse. Requires IWolverineRuntime, IEnvelopeLifecycle, and message contract types.
