TITLE: Testing End-to-End Batch Message Processing with Wolverine in C#
DESCRIPTION: Presents a full integration test to ensure that multiple Item messages published are batched and processed as an Item[] array by Wolverine. Utilizes xUnit for the test method and Wolverine's test helpers to publish, track, and assert batch delivery. Dependencies include xUnit and the Wolverine test framework; published messages are verified to arrive as a single batch. This verifies both correct batching and item delivery, ensuring test driven confidence.
