TITLE: Initializing Program.cs for Minimal Web API with Wolverine - C#
DESCRIPTION: This Program.cs file configures a minimal ASP.NET Core Web API, integrates Wolverine as a mediator, adds Swashbuckle for API docs, and registers singleton repositories. It maps two POST endpoints that delegate commands to Wolverine for processing, and configures Oakton for command line diagnostics. Requires .NET 6+, Wolverine, Oakton, and Swashbuckle packages; endpoints accept command objects and return async operation results.
