SOURCE: https://github.com/jasperfx/wolverine/blob/main/docs/guide/durability/dead-letter-storage.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
update wolverine_dead_letters set replayable = true where exception_type = 'InvalidAccountException';
```

